snippet.title: Shall We Date- Lost Island Lionel Chapter 01
snippet.description: I remember playing this game years ago when it was called 'Shall We Date Lost Island' and 'Shall We Date Lost Island+' back when they were single apps and 'Story Jar' didn't exist. However now 'NTT Solmare' have developed an app, 'Story Jar' where you can play nearly all of their games in one place for free, with additional purchases of course. 'Story Jar' is absolutely amazing and ALL DUE CREDIT FOR THIS VIDEO GOES TO 'NTT SOLMARE', I OWN NOTHING IN THE VIDEO NEITHER AM I UPLOADING FOR PROFIT.
